{{Infobox dungeon |name = Fullmoon Island |image = [[File:Fullmoon Island.png|300px]] |caption = A bird's-eye view of Fullmoon Island. |tokens = 96,500 |location = The leftmost island off the northwestern coast of Sinnoh. }} '''Fullmoon Island''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Sinnoh]]. It initially has 64 tiles arranged in an 8x8 square, including 8 chest tiles, 19 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 2,653,000 HP.
